WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:12.404 --> 00:00:16.160
Yogi intro:

00:00:16.160 --> 00:00:20.320
...which has been programmed and set up,
and at that moment it becomes plugged

00:00:20.320 --> 00:00:23.440
into the mains, and it becomes connected.

00:00:23.440 --> 00:00:27.040
That's the moment of actualisation.

00:00:27.040 --> 00:00:30.560
That's the moment when you become
your Spirit.

00:00:30.560 --> 00:00:33.360
This is what we've been seeking.

00:00:34.720 --> 00:00:42.720
There's no mesmerism,
no intellectual dissertations.

00:00:42.720 --> 00:00:44.320
It's a reality, and it's happening.

00:00:44.320 --> 00:00:46.560
It's happening on a mass scale.

00:00:46.560 --> 00:00:52.000
This is the first time Mataji has been
to America since 1972.

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:54.080
She came on a visit at that time.

00:00:54.080 --> 00:00:59.040
But all over the world, Sahaja Yoga,
as it's called, is taking root.

00:00:59.040 --> 00:01:03.600
Thousands upon thousands of people
are getting their realisation.

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:07.280
And when they get it, they're developing
it and settling into it.

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:09.760
Their life is being transformed.

00:01:09.760 --> 00:01:13.440
Physical and emotional problems
just fall away.

00:01:13.440 --> 00:01:15.120
You start to feel the joy of life.

00:01:15.120 --> 00:01:19.360
You can cope with the tensions
and stresses of living.

00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:22.080
And you look at the whole
of human existence

00:01:22.080 --> 00:01:24.640
as almost like a bit of a joke.

00:01:25.520 --> 00:01:33.600
You cope with the problems
in a very wonderful way.

00:01:33.600 --> 00:01:35.920
The other beautiful thing
about Self-realisation

00:01:35.920 --> 00:01:41.200
is that as you get it,
you can give it to others.

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:45.440
One light is enlightened,
it can enlighten another light.

00:01:45.440 --> 00:01:46.960
And this is the way it has to be.

00:01:46.960 --> 00:01:50.880
It's nothing exclusive.
It's nothing that money can buy.

00:01:51.600 --> 00:01:55.680
And now, as Mother often says,
on the tree of life

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:59.760
at first there were very, very few
flowers that turned to fruit.

00:01:59.760 --> 00:02:04.960
Now all the flowers have come,
the blossom time has come.

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:10.160
And many, many of those flowers
have to turn to fruit.

00:02:10.160 --> 00:02:13.200
This is the right of the seekers.

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:19.760
This is the right which you've earned
and which you must pursue.

00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:24.240
Mother has nothing to gain from this.

00:02:24.240 --> 00:02:25.760
She travels around the world.

00:02:25.760 --> 00:02:35.440
She is a mother, she is a grandmother,
she is the wife of an important

00:02:35.440 --> 00:02:37.440
Secretary General
of the United Nations.

00:02:37.440 --> 00:02:43.600
So she has no basis for needing
any support of any kind from us.

00:02:43.600 --> 00:02:45.120
She only gives.

00:02:45.120 --> 00:02:49.840
And in giving, she is giving nothing
but love and compassion.

00:02:49.840 --> 00:02:51.840
And that's the power of Divine Love.

00:02:51.840 --> 00:02:57.760
That's the power of a great spiritual
being to awaken that which is within us

00:02:57.760 --> 00:03:00.000
and which is our right.

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:03.680
So during this lecture
simply slip your shoes off

00:03:03.680 --> 00:03:09.440
and hold your hands out in this fashion
so that you can actually become

00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:13.920
earthed to the earth.
That's the purpose.

00:03:13.920 --> 00:03:18.240
It's as simple as that.

00:03:18.240 --> 00:03:22.480
It's a very, very basic
electrical circuitry.

00:03:25.760 --> 00:03:28.800
And just simply hold the hands out
in that fashion

00:03:28.800 --> 00:03:32.160
as if asking for something,
as if asking for something.

00:03:32.160 --> 00:03:33.200
It's as simple as that.

00:03:33.200 --> 00:03:38.960
And what you perhaps begin to find
is that during the talk

00:03:38.960 --> 00:03:40.800
you'll start to feel the vibrations.

00:03:40.800 --> 00:03:43.600
These vibrations are the vibrations
which have been spoken of

00:03:43.600 --> 00:03:45.120
in all the scriptures.

00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:49.440
If you're a Christian it speaks
of the cool wind of the Holy Spirit.

00:03:49.440 --> 00:03:54.400
If you're a Muslim it's the Ruh.
And so it goes on.

00:03:54.400 --> 00:04:01.120
So again I'll introduce to you
our mother, Mataji Nirmala Devi.

00:04:01.120 --> 00:04:05.760
Shri Mataji: It’s really unbelievable isn’t it?
It sounds so fantastic.

00:04:05.760 --> 00:04:13.200
I have been here about nine years back
and I told them that, "It’s within you,

00:04:13.200 --> 00:04:16.160
there’s a simplest thing,
is a living process;

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:21.120
it works out, for nothing at all.
It’s your own."

00:04:21.120 --> 00:04:25.440
But what I found, that Americans
were still busy guru shopping;

00:04:25.440 --> 00:04:29.280
they wanted to go through that,
they wanted to do all that.

00:04:29.280 --> 00:04:30.240
What could I do?

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:32.480
I told them, "You don’t have to do
all this.

00:04:32.480 --> 00:04:35.920
Why do you want to waste your energy?
Why do you want to waste your money?

00:04:35.920 --> 00:04:38.640
Nothing, you just have it!"
But they wouldn’t.

00:04:38.640 --> 00:04:41.680
They wanted to spend their money –
they had the money that time,

00:04:41.680 --> 00:04:48.160
they thought they can buy some bhagwans
and gods and things like that.

00:04:48.160 --> 00:04:52.240
All sorts of things were on when I came
here, and they wouldn’t listen to me.

00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:54.080
They wouldn’t listen to me.

00:04:54.080 --> 00:04:57.760
I said, "You cannot purchase it,
you cannot buy it.

00:04:57.760 --> 00:05:00.480
They are misleading you."

00:05:00.480 --> 00:05:06.160
So I thought, better to retire
for some time from America.

00:05:06.160 --> 00:05:09.280
But in India now, in the villages,
we have thousands of people

00:05:09.280 --> 00:05:12.080
who have got realization – it’s so simple.

00:05:12.080 --> 00:05:16.560
You are seekers, you are seekers
because the time has come

00:05:16.560 --> 00:05:19.920
that you have to be here
and that you have to get your realization.

00:05:19.920 --> 00:05:21.360
It’s very simple.

00:05:21.360 --> 00:05:24.480
After all, God has created
this great world;

00:05:24.480 --> 00:05:27.760
this creation is His own
and He has to save it.

00:05:27.760 --> 00:05:32.400
Jolly well, He has to do it.

00:05:32.400 --> 00:05:36.480
But it is so incredible,
they can’t believe it, it’s impossible.

00:05:36.480 --> 00:05:39.360
They think, "How can that be?
We must stand on our heads,"

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:42.320
or, "We have to pay a lot of money,
we have to become broke,

00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:46.640
we have to give up this, give up that.
Do all sorts of nonsensical things

00:05:46.640 --> 00:05:51.200
and then, what we find?
We are left high and dry."

00:05:51.200 --> 00:05:53.680
It’s true, I know, it’s true.

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:57.440
But you could have avoided it;
when I came here,

00:05:57.440 --> 00:06:02.240
I told people very,
very clearly and plainly.

00:06:02.240 --> 00:06:04.400
But I was amazed, also,
apart from this:

00:06:04.400 --> 00:06:09.840
they did all kinds of funny things
about what I announced to them.

00:06:09.840 --> 00:06:11.760
I said that you are to be born again.

00:06:11.760 --> 00:06:16.960
Alright, they taped me
and they started organizations

00:06:16.960 --> 00:06:20.480
with this name that,
"We are born again" –

00:06:20.480 --> 00:06:25.040
they certified themselves
and they started another organization

00:06:25.040 --> 00:06:28.720
with some vibrations,
something [UNCLEAR Sun]

00:06:28.720 --> 00:06:34.240
instead of being honest to yourself
and getting the thing down to Earth.

00:06:34.240 --> 00:06:37.520
I didn’t know why they were getting
into these hallucinations

00:06:37.520 --> 00:06:42.983
which is imaginary things.
We have to be just honest to ourselves. That's all.

00:06:42.983 --> 00:06:46.560
It's so simple. It’s extremely simple.

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:49.280
But when you go to these places
and do that,

00:06:49.280 --> 00:06:52.800
you get damaged, you really get damaged.

00:06:52.800 --> 00:06:57.600
Of course the task is very difficult now for me,
I find, comparatively.

00:06:58.320 --> 00:07:00.400
It would have been much better
[UNCLEAR] no doubt.

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:06.640
But they won’t listen to me,
even up to the point

00:07:06.640 --> 00:07:09.680
that they said, "You must charge
some money.

00:07:09.680 --> 00:07:11.920
People are doing it for so much,
so much.

00:07:11.920 --> 00:07:14.800
At least charge some money or then
people will have no value for it."

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:18.360
I said, "If they start valuing it
in money, they’ll never value it."

00:07:18.360 --> 00:07:22.880
It should not be done;
whatever is wrong should not be done.

00:07:22.880 --> 00:07:26.880
And they just wouldn’t accept it;
it’s such a funny situation.

00:07:26.880 --> 00:07:32.240
That’s how I went back;
nine years I waited.

00:07:32.240 --> 00:07:38.160
But Americans are great seekers,
they are, despite all these damages.

00:07:40.320 --> 00:07:42.320
We had a very good experience
the other day,

00:07:42.320 --> 00:07:46.160
with all these people who were there.

00:07:46.160 --> 00:07:51.440
Especially, we went to Boston where
there were about fifty-four people or so,

00:07:51.440 --> 00:07:54.720
and fifty of them got realization,
just like that.

00:07:54.720 --> 00:08:00.640
Fifty of them, can you believe it?
I was amazed. It’s expanding.

00:08:00.640 --> 00:08:04.080
Consolidation may be a problem,
but that should be consolidated.

00:08:04.080 --> 00:08:11.360
I did give realization to some here,
and they were quite funny.

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:14.720
They started charging people
for their vibrations.

00:08:14.720 --> 00:08:18.080
Just imagine?
They got it without any payment

00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:21.360
or anything, but they started
charging people for it,

00:08:21.360 --> 00:08:24.560
and when they came to India, we found
out they had lost their vibrations.

00:08:24.560 --> 00:08:26.960
They were very heated-up people
and we told them,

00:08:26.960 --> 00:08:29.600
"You cannot charge for it.
How do you charge?"

00:08:29.600 --> 00:08:30.880
He said, "How are we to live?"

00:08:30.880 --> 00:08:35.280
I said, "How did you live before?
Live like that."

00:08:35.280 --> 00:08:37.200
"Oh, we were schoolteachers, we were…"

00:08:37.200 --> 00:08:41.040
I said, "Do that. You cannot charge
for these vibrations;

00:08:41.040 --> 00:08:43.520
these are Divine, this is love,
you cannot charge.

00:08:43.520 --> 00:08:48.640
How can you sell that?
Can you sell your love?"

00:08:48.640 --> 00:08:51.200
It’s a simple thing Americans
have to understand,

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:53.920
that you cannot sell it.

00:08:53.920 --> 00:08:58.800
It’s too simple for them to understand,
that there could be someone who really

00:08:58.800 --> 00:09:01.600
loves, just loves for love’s sake.

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:04.480
There could be one, at least,
like that in this whole world.

00:09:04.480 --> 00:09:07.520
If they understand this,
then it will be easy for them

00:09:07.520 --> 00:09:11.200
to understand that all these things
are built-in you;

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:14.480
they are already made like that.
It’s not at all difficult.

00:09:14.480 --> 00:09:18.480
Like a candle which is made properly
and there’s a wick;

00:09:18.480 --> 00:09:22.640
it’s very easy to enlighten that
if you are enlightened.

00:09:23.520 --> 00:09:26.640
What do you do?
What goes out of this candle?

00:09:26.640 --> 00:09:32.400
It’s nothing. You just enlighten
another light without any difficulties.

00:09:32.400 --> 00:09:37.600
It’s nothing special, nothing great;
it’s very, very simple.

00:09:37.600 --> 00:09:40.800
But we want to make everything
complicated, and what am I to do?

00:09:40.800 --> 00:09:43.200
If you have to eat your food,
you eat like this, isn’t it?

00:09:43.200 --> 00:09:45.600
Do you put your hand down like that?

00:09:45.600 --> 00:09:49.280
If you have to breathe,
which is so vital; it is the simplest.

00:09:49.280 --> 00:09:52.080
Do you go to libraries
to read how to breathe?

00:09:52.960 --> 00:09:55.200
It’s all so simple, you won’t believe.

00:09:55.200 --> 00:09:57.520
Like sprouting a seed,
it’s a living process;

00:09:57.520 --> 00:10:04.400
it has to be simple, spontaneous.
How can it be complicated?

00:10:04.400 --> 00:10:09.520
Then, another problem is that here,
people read a lot about God.

00:10:09.520 --> 00:10:12.560
You can’t read about Him,
you have to know it.

00:10:12.560 --> 00:10:15.760
They just read, "This is the God,
that is the God."

00:10:16.880 --> 00:10:20.640
Today we met somebody who said that,
"I believe in a man

00:10:20.640 --> 00:10:22.000
who calls himself Jesus."

00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:25.360
I said, "Very good, put him on the water.
Can he walk on the water?

00:10:25.360 --> 00:10:27.680
If he can walk on the water,
alright, he’s Jesus.

00:10:27.680 --> 00:10:30.160
But does he walk?
Put him on the water."

00:10:30.160 --> 00:10:34.800
It’s very simple. If I say I am something,
I must do it, isn’t it?

00:10:34.800 --> 00:10:38.080
If somebody says, "I can make you fly,"
you start paying him money;

00:10:38.080 --> 00:10:43.280
such a lot of money goes to this fellow.
Does he fly?

00:10:43.280 --> 00:10:44.640
If he flies, then he can teach you.

00:10:44.640 --> 00:10:47.200
If he does not know himself how to fly,
how will he teach you?

00:10:47.760 --> 00:10:51.440
It’s a very logical thing:
you have to know that

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:55.760
we are not going to fly anymore now.
We have flown as birds,

00:10:55.760 --> 00:10:59.520
so we are not going to fly or hop –
we have been that.

00:10:59.520 --> 00:11:04.880
We are going to become something more
in our awareness.

00:11:04.880 --> 00:11:09.920
We see the simple thing we should know
that we have to become that.

00:11:09.920 --> 00:11:14.000
Something in our own awareness,
something has to happen

00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:27.280
that should make us something that we are,
that we should become the Absolute.

00:11:27.280 --> 00:11:30.640
We are not what we are,
we are something else –

00:11:30.640 --> 00:11:37.120
we are like our, say, mind,
we are our rationality which can go anywhere.

00:11:37.120 --> 00:11:38.320
It’s not Absolute.

00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:40.880
Supposing somebody comes here,
a Mr. XYZ and says,

00:11:40.880 --> 00:11:43.920
"This is a very nice car."
Another one will come and say,

00:11:43.920 --> 00:11:48.960
"Oh, it’s not so good." Another one say,
"Maybe good, maybe."

00:11:48.960 --> 00:11:51.760
Three human beings, all of them
are human beings.

00:11:51.760 --> 00:11:54.000
They are not animals,
they are human beings

00:11:54.720 --> 00:11:57.760
from the same place,
from the same village, you can take it.

00:11:57.760 --> 00:12:02.400
Put them together,
they will have three opinions.

00:12:02.400 --> 00:12:05.160
If they continue to have criteria,
we shall say –

00:12:05.160 --> 00:12:10.880
see they can have even thousand,
if they change. So why?

00:12:10.880 --> 00:12:14.240
Because they have not got
their absolute values.

00:12:14.240 --> 00:12:19.120
there must be something absolute
within us, when you start [INAUDIBLE],

00:12:19.120 --> 00:12:22.720
you start feeling the absolute.

00:12:22.720 --> 00:12:25.120
As he said, really it happens to you.

00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:29.760
You become that in no time,
and you can feel it –

00:12:29.760 --> 00:12:34.400
on your hands, on your fingers –
the reality.

00:12:34.400 --> 00:12:36.320
You ask a simple question,
"Is there God?"

00:12:36.320 --> 00:12:40.160
Somebody told me,
"I don’t believe in Christ."

00:12:40.160 --> 00:12:43.840
I said, "Alright, why? Have you seen Him?
Why don’t you believe?"

00:12:43.840 --> 00:12:45.120
"I don’t believe."

00:12:45.120 --> 00:12:47.520
"But why? What is the reason?"

00:12:47.520 --> 00:12:49.840
"I believe in this
and I don’t believe in that."

00:12:49.840 --> 00:12:54.160
"Well, why? Is there any absolute
by which you have judged

00:12:54.160 --> 00:12:57.360
whether there was Christ or not?
Whether it was true or not?

00:12:57.360 --> 00:13:01.600
Whether it’s just a myth?"

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:02.720
"No, I have not."

00:13:02.720 --> 00:13:07.520
"Then how can you say ‘I believe’?’
You keep yourself open!"

00:13:07.520 --> 00:13:11.920
First, you become your Self –
that’s like Buddha.

00:13:11.920 --> 00:13:17.040
He said, "Don’t talk of God or anything.
First of all, let them become the Self.

00:13:17.040 --> 00:13:19.360
If they become the Self,
then talk of other things.

00:13:19.360 --> 00:13:21.920
Because if they do not, if you talk
of something else,

00:13:21.920 --> 00:13:26.080
they will come out with their own ideas,
that, ‘I don’t believe in God,

00:13:26.080 --> 00:13:28.320
I don’t believe in this,
I don’t believe in that.’ "

00:13:28.320 --> 00:13:31.280
So He said, "Alright,
you become your Self,

00:13:31.280 --> 00:13:34.080
that’s the first thing.
Once you become your Self,

00:13:34.080 --> 00:13:37.840
then you will start seeing other things
through your awareness,

00:13:37.840 --> 00:13:39.840
which is something special."

00:13:39.840 --> 00:13:44.960
And that’s what should happen to you;
is to first become your Self.

00:13:44.960 --> 00:13:49.840
Then you start judging other things
because now you have that awareness

00:13:49.840 --> 00:13:52.800
by which you can judge.

00:13:52.800 --> 00:13:56.640
How are we to know that –
supposing these vibrations come to us –

00:13:56.640 --> 00:13:59.440
whether they are absolute our not?

00:13:59.440 --> 00:14:03.200
After all, we should find out
whether they are absolute or not.

00:14:03.200 --> 00:14:08.160
For that, we can use a method
which is I call as a relative method.

00:14:08.160 --> 00:14:13.960
Today I told them that you get two boys
who are from a lunatic asylum –

00:14:13.960 --> 00:14:15.440
certified mad people.

00:14:18.160 --> 00:14:21.600
Then get two people
who have got cancer,

00:14:22.160 --> 00:14:26.240
and then get two people, one realized
soul and one un-realized soul –

00:14:26.240 --> 00:14:29.520
according to me, one is realized,
and one is un-realized.

00:14:30.640 --> 00:14:34.480
Now you put all of them to me
and ask them to see their vibrations.

00:14:34.480 --> 00:14:40.240
You will find the person who is mad –
he will start doing all kinds of actions;

00:14:43.360 --> 00:14:49.440
he may feel shaking all over the body;
his whole body might shake like this;

00:14:49.440 --> 00:14:50.880
the whole thing might [UNCLEAR].

00:14:51.680 --> 00:14:53.920
The person with the cancer
will feel terrible heat

00:14:53.920 --> 00:14:58.640
getting out of his body, a heat so much
so, it happens sometimes,

00:14:58.640 --> 00:15:03.680
that the room does not need a heater –
in London, even during wintertime.

00:15:03.680 --> 00:15:06.880
Now, you have another one
who is not a realized soul.

00:15:06.880 --> 00:15:10.000
Such a person may a little bit feel hot,
or something,

00:15:10.000 --> 00:15:13.360
and after some time he starts feeling
the cool breeze, gradually,

00:15:13.360 --> 00:15:14.000
for a little bit.

00:15:14.000 --> 00:15:16.240
Then you have a realized soul
and a little child sitting.

00:15:16.240 --> 00:15:18.320
He said, "I was [UNCLEAR taking] it
when I entered here.

00:15:18.320 --> 00:15:20.160
Yes it is there, I know it is there."

00:15:22.400 --> 00:15:26.880
It’s so simple because it is vital.
It’s important;

00:15:26.880 --> 00:15:30.720
evolution is the most important thing.

00:15:30.720 --> 00:15:35.120
That’s how we have become human beings
and you have to become something higher.

00:15:35.120 --> 00:15:40.560
It’s all placed within us very nicely,
very safe, very protected.

00:15:40.560 --> 00:15:43.360
But, of course, we go headlong
into every sort of thing

00:15:43.360 --> 00:15:46.080
and naturally we get damaged.

00:15:46.080 --> 00:15:48.240
With all these beautiful things
within us,

