you can have from these people.

01:05:04.960 --> 01:05:10.400
Now, it’s all on the left hand,
it’s working out, it’s alright.

01:05:10.400 --> 01:05:16.000
Now, let’s have your hands towards me
and close your eyes.

01:05:24.240 --> 01:05:31.120
Put both the feet on the ground.

01:05:31.120 --> 01:05:41.600
Both the hands towards me
and close your eyes; don’t open your eyes,

01:05:41.600 --> 01:05:47.280
because when the Kundalini rushes
through this centre of Agnya,

01:05:47.280 --> 01:05:52.080
then there is dilation of the pupils
and, if you keep your eyes open,

01:05:52.080 --> 01:05:56.400
it won’t come up. Close your eyes.

01:05:56.400 --> 01:06:05.120
This happening takes place
and your attention is drawn inside.

01:08:21.760 --> 01:08:30.800
Put your right hand on your heart.
Close your eyes.

01:08:30.800 --> 01:08:36.800
Ask a question to me,
"Mother, am I the Spirit?"

01:08:36.800 --> 01:08:40.080
Mother, am I the Spirit?

01:08:40.080 --> 01:08:41.760
Three times.

01:08:41.760 --> 01:08:44.160
Mother, am I the Spirit?

01:08:44.160 --> 01:08:45.440
Again.

01:08:45.440 --> 01:08:54.640
Mother, am I the Spirit?

01:08:54.640 --> 01:08:57.680
Now say, "Mother, I am not guilty."

01:08:57.680 --> 01:09:10.560
(Seekers repeat three times)

01:09:10.560 --> 01:09:18.224
Now, you have to ask for realization.
Say, "Mother, please give me my realization."

01:09:18.224 --> 01:09:23.920
(Seekers repeat three times)

01:10:43.040 --> 01:10:58.000
(Still a little bit left.)

01:11:14.160 --> 01:11:16.880
Now please say,
"Mother, I forgive everyone."

01:11:16.880 --> 01:11:20.720
Got it? Good.

01:11:20.720 --> 01:11:27.280
(Seekers repeat three times)

01:11:29.040 --> 01:11:36.000
Now you have to say,
"Mother, if I have neglected my Spirit,

01:11:36.000 --> 01:11:37.840
please forgive me."

01:11:42.000 --> 01:11:53.840
(Seekers repeat three times)

01:11:55.200 --> 01:12:01.280
Alright?&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:12:03.120 --> 01:12:25.503
That’s it, it will work out.
Keep your eyes shut.

01:12:25.503 --> 01:12:29.360
The Sahaja yogis can see now. Got it?

01:12:29.360 --> 01:12:31.920
Just put your right hand …
yes, he has Mother.

01:12:31.920 --> 01:12:34.000
Just put your right hand above your head.

01:12:34.000 --> 01:12:39.280
You got it. You can feel it on your head
if you have got it.

01:12:39.280 --> 01:12:40.880
All the Sahaja yogis can come and see.

01:12:40.880 --> 01:12:53.360
Feel ok? It’s coming out of the top
of your head? You feeling it there?

01:12:53.360 --> 01:12:56.880
Those who have been to other gurus
should say, "Mother, I am my own guru."

01:12:56.880 --> 01:13:00.457
I can feel his, the same – he’s got it,
he’s got it.

01:13:00.457 --> 01:13:01.440
Yes, yes you can feel. He’s got it,
she knows.

01:13:01.440 --> 01:13:02.480
I don’t even have to feel it …

01:13:02.480 --> 01:13:03.600
Are you feeling it on your hands?

01:13:03.600 --> 01:13:06.800
It’s coming all out of you.

01:13:06.800 --> 01:13:22.240
(laughing) Yes, Yes, he’s got it, yes.
Have you got it?

01:13:22.240 --> 01:13:25.520
You didn’t say anything.
You were keeping quiet.

01:13:25.520 --> 01:13:27.760
You should have said it.
You are catching on the Vishuddhi,

01:13:27.760 --> 01:13:31.840
and if you had said it,
it would have opened up. Alright,

01:13:31.840 --> 01:13:38.320
we’ll work it out. You should get it.
We can work it out.

01:13:42.560 --> 01:13:48.240
Now are you feeling it? Slowly, slowly,
it’s a very subtle thing.

01:13:49.840 --> 01:13:54.640
But in the second sitting it is better,
isn’t it? It’s more clear. It’s very clear.

01:13:54.640 --> 01:13:59.280
Oh, it’s hot, alright.
You’re alright now, are you?

01:13:59.280 --> 01:14:03.360
It’s a pity they can’t turn the air
conditioning – the air conditioning’s

01:14:03.360 --> 01:14:04.480
causing a lot of disturbance.

01:14:04.480 --> 01:14:07.840
No, no, no – it’s alright.
You believe it, it is there.

01:14:07.840 --> 01:14:13.200
yesterday, somebody who got it
thought that the window was open,

01:14:14.080 --> 01:14:19.360
and then he went into the cellar to see,
and still it was there.

01:14:19.360 --> 01:14:28.116
Are you alright now? Good! I’m very happy
the second sitting you got it. It’s good.

01:14:28.116 --> 01:14:29.600
So changed, so changed.
Look at this gentleman.

01:14:29.600 --> 01:14:33.840
Are you alright now? See, you have got it;
second sitting, you have got it.

01:14:33.840 --> 01:14:39.200
Now, what about this gentleman –
you got it?

01:14:41.440 --> 01:14:46.360
Did you feel, my child? No?
Alright, I’ll work it out.

01:14:46.360 --> 01:14:52.461
She’s feeling it in her left,
but not in her right. She thinks too much.

01:14:52.461 --> 01:14:54.760
Agnya was, too … that’s why I said
we stop it there!

01:14:54.760 --> 01:14:57.360
That should work it out. Here,
keep your eyes shut.

01:14:57.360 --> 01:15:00.800
Now, you have to forgive;
go on forgiving – "I forgive", say.

01:15:00.800 --> 01:15:01.440
How easy is that?

01:15:01.440 --> 01:15:02.480
I forgive

01:15:02.480 --> 01:15:03.360
Again

01:15:03.360 --> 01:15:05.440
(seeker repeats twice)

01:15:05.440 --> 01:15:19.920
I forgive everyone.
(seeker repeats, Shri Mataji is working on her –

01:15:19.920 --> 01:15:20.316
Forgive, forgive, forgive.)

01:15:20.316 --> 01:15:24.640
Ah, forgiving’s not there – now forgive.

01:15:29.440 --> 01:15:45.501
(Shri Mataji and the yogis continue
to work on all the seekers)

